Absorption has never been a flat reduction in he total damage. It is factored against the weapon damage itself I believe.<P>So a 20 pt damage 2 hand weapon is reduced to an 18 pt before all the final damage calculations if i am not mistaken. This is a pretty huge boost for a class that has existed for the entire duration of the game pretty much at 0% Abs.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
