Don't underestimate this change.  Mages will be tougher than rogue classes and maybe healers, because they have a personal bladeturn.  Did you ever notice that Archers will sometimes go for a rogue or cleric over a mage?  Mages BT absorbs that first crit that can kill a rogue or even a healer in one shot.  This change helps even out the playing field.
