The good...this is huge. Seems to be very nice. Still don't have full numberes, but....<P>The bad.<P>Some high spec individuals is actually seeing LESS of an AF bonus than they recieved before. Used to be Spec level adjusted the AF of a buff. Yes this means high matter spec gave you higher AF from your buff, MUCH higher in some cases.<P>NOw some single spec Wizzies are seeing a decrease in their AF. NOw the buffs are a flat rate, unaffected by spec level. This means neglecting it (like most sorcerors and matter) will no longer make your defense paper thin, but going beyond the 50% spec mark no longer ADDs to the AF either.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
