You are correct. it normalizes it, as yu had to have high matter or Earth to see the AF bonus rise. but it DID rise, and it was actually higher than it is now for a heavy earth spec. By almost 50 points at level 40 or so.<P>But, AF is nowhere NEAR as important as Abs anyway. AF is avoiding being hit, which is great. but the difference between 380 and 420 is negligible by the time casters get that high, as tanks are ranking well in to the 800 and 900 range.<P>So again it looks like one small portion of what we do was adjusted down, but the overall effectiveness has actually risen again.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
